ZH: 那个城市里有一座高塔。
EN: There is a tall tower in that city.

ZH: 这座塔已经有一千年的历史了。
EN: This tower has a history of one thousand years.

ZH: 塔顶上的旗帜在风中飘扬。
EN: The flag on top of the tower is waving in the wind.

ZH: 塔身上雕刻着很多花纹。
EN: There are many carvings on the tower.

ZH: 这座塔是用石头建造的。
EN: This tower is built with stone.

ZH: 大雨把整座塔淋得湿透了。
EN: The heavy rain soaked the entire tower.

ZH: 每年很多游客都会登上这座塔。
EN: Many tourists climb up this tower every year.

ZH: 夜晚塔灯照亮了整个城市。
EN: The tower lights up the whole city at night.

ZH: 塔下有一个美丽的花园。
EN: There is a beautiful garden below the tower.

ZH: 工人们正在修缮这座古老的塔。
EN: Workers are repairing this ancient tower.

ZH: 塔身镶嵌着五彩的琉璃。
EN: The tower is embedded with colorful glass.

ZH: 传说中这座塔藏着宝藏。
EN: It is said that this tower hides a treasure.

ZH: 塔楼里有一个观景台。
EN: There is an observation deck in the tower.

ZH: 塔内有很多历史文物陈列。
EN: There are many historical artifacts displayed in the tower.

ZH: 塔下有一条古老的街道。
EN: There is an ancient street below the tower.

ZH: 塔尖上的尖顶闪闪发光。
EN: The spire on the top of the tower is sparkling.

ZH: 这座塔曾经是城市的标志。
EN: This tower used to be the symbol of the city.

ZH: 在清晨，塔影倒映在湖面上。
EN: In the morning, the reflection of the tower is on the lake.

ZH: 塔根下有一个小喷泉。
EN: There is a small fountain at the base of the tower.

ZH: 塔外面有一个纪念碑。
EN: There is a monument outside the tower.
